hopobject.body: What part of do you come from? ofloxacin ear drops pregnancy In 2005, my insurance company case manager suggested I might like to move to a nursing home. No way! My health insurance company wanted to stop paying for what little home nursing I had. This was a big deal for my health and I couldn’t afford to pay for nursing on my own. I got a lawyer who specialized in disability cases, and we decided to ask for full-time nursing. We were quickly denied by the insurance company.
